Keeping up with the latest tech and gadgets can be a burden on your wallet, especially if you live in a country where high-end hardware is expensive. The price of top tech items can vary greatly across different countries and while certain products may be priced in line with international standards, other tech may be disproportionately pricey. We’ve compared the pricing of four top-of-the-range tech products in the following countries to see how South Africa stacks up: Currencies were converted to South African rand using the exchange rate on 25 January 2017.    